OL,6,FLord Graham Brady's been speaking to
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports political
OL,8,Fcorrespondent Lise McNally at the
OL,9,FConservative party's conference in
OL,10,FBirmingham.
OL,12,FHe is the former Member of Parliament
OL,13,Fwho for many years was the leader of a
OL,14,Fgroup of backbench MPs with the power
OL,15,Fto choose not just new leaders of the
OL,16,FConservative Party but Prime Ministers
OL,17,Ftoo.
OL,19,FLord Graham Brady, the former MP for
OL,20,FSale and Altrincham West, presided
OL,21,Fover the influential 1922 committee.
