OL,6,FOver 14 years he saw five Prime
OL,7,FMinisters, the EU referendum, the
OL,8,FCovid pandemic and the war in Ukraine.
OL,10,FIt is fair to say his time in office
OL,11,Fhas been busy and his new memoir is
OL,12,Faptly called "Kingmaker".
OL,14,FLord Brady said he learned "early on"
OL,15,Fto keep his counsel in the role, but
OL,16,Fthere were now "important things to
OL,17,Fget on record".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
