OL,6,FHe said he also wanted to "dispel some
OL,7,Fmyths", as some people had used his
OL,8,Ftaciturn approach "to speculate and
OL,9,Fclaim certain things".
OL,11,FLord Brady was also keen to correct
OL,12,Fthe "false rumour" Rishi Sunak called
OL,13,Fthe General Election early because he
OL,14,Fwas facing an imminent vote of no
OL,15,Fconfidence.
OL,17,F"As I revealed in the book, I had 10
OL,18,Fletters in my safe, not the 53 that
OL,19,Fwould be necessary to trigger a vote,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
