OL,6,F"Rishi Sunak did not call an election
OL,7,Fearly because he was facing imminent
OL,8,Fvote of no confidence."
OL,10,FMuch of Lord Brady's work in
OL,11,FWestminster largely played out in the
OL,12,Fshadows. He saw much, and said little
OL,13,Fbut through his memoirs he is now
OL,14,Fshedding some light on one of the
OL,15,Fwildest periods in political history
OL,17,FLord Brady said: "I've kept diaries
OL,18,Fthrough the whole of my time in
OL,19,FParliament over nearly three decades.
