OL,6,F"And of course, I never expected to
OL,7,Fhave quite such an exciting period as
OL,8,Fthe years of turbulence over the last
OL,9,Ffew years.
OL,11,F"But during those times, the number of
OL,12,Fpeople who stopped me in the street
OL,13,Fsaying, 'I do hope you're going to
OL,14,Fwrite a book'. I felt I ought to
OL,15,Foblige.
OL,17,F"I think I've put some things which
OL,18,Fwill be of value and interest to
OL,19,Fpolitical scientists and historians as
OL,20,Fwell."
