OL,6,FHistorians studying the last few years
OL,7,Fwill certainly be kept busy.
OL,9,FWho is Lord Graham Brady?
OL,11,FBorn in Salford in 1967, Lord Brady
OL,12,Ffirst became active in the
OL,13,FConservative Party aged just 16.
OL,15,FIn 1997, shortly before his 30th
OL,16,Fbirthday, he was elected MP for
OL,17,FAltrincham and Sale West in Greater
OL,18,FManchester, becoming what was then the
OL,19,Fparty's youngest MP.
