OL,6,FIn 2010, he was elected chairman of
OL,7,Fthe 1922 Committee, a role he held
OL,8,Funchallenged for 14 years making him
OL,9,Fthe longest serving chairman in the
OL,10,Fcommittee's history.
OL,12,FThe group - known in Westminster as
OL,13,Fthe "men in grey suits" - meets weekly
OL,14,Fand discusses the view of the party's
OL,15,Fbackbench MPs.
